I am a sucker for alternate history. This gets an upvote, although there is one suggestion I have (less criticism and more something I wish it had). I'd love some sort of listing of where history diverged from baseline reality and some interesting events post-divergence. I also agree with some of the others that the conflict at the end seems abrupt and a lackluster ending for what is a fantastically executed build up. I want more. At the mention of the possible mission to steal some of their tech, my brain went down a rabbit hole of MTF logs, missions gone sideways, and a plot twist at the end where it's discovered that beneath the seemingly utopian facade, something evil is lurking. Aka all the cliches you could possibly use. This is why I don't write SCPs.





